When In Doubt

Reference the spec docs in /docs for business logic details.
Reference screenshots in /design-reference for UI patterns.
Keep it simple. Ship working code. Polish later.
Every feature should work on mobile first. Desktop is the expanded view.
Never sacrifice page load speed for visual complexity.
When choosing between a clever solution and a readable solution, choose readable.
